As you may have noticed from the news on @palacenftbot about the use of NFT 2.0 in stickers, prices for collections are steadily rising. This growth is a direct response to exclusive leaks about the upcoming launch of NFT 2.0.

But please note:
It is not worth comparing the current growth with that of June. In June, we were growing based solely on promises, but now there is even direct evidence that NFT 2.0 is ready. If, as promised, we see NFT 2.0 within 10 days, minting will follow 100%.

What is so revolutionary about NFT 2.0 (based on available information and leaks)?

Unified Control: All marketplaces will operate through a single aggregator that strictly controls the smart contract.

Combating ‚Äòcircumvention‚Äô: The system is designed to protect the commissions of authors and platforms. Any attempts to circumvent them through third-party scripts will become impossible.

I believe that the commission clause is the most important one, because why would large projects promote their collections if they don't get anything in return? Pudgy Penguins' deliberate omission of their stickers is related to this very issue.

Closed Ecosystem: NFT 2.0 can ONLY be sold on specialised platforms integrated with this smart contract.

Fundamental changes are coming. Have we finally waited long enough?

Yesterday, [Sticker Community](https://t.me/sticker_community) was presented at the OxConnect festival in Saint Petersburg!

The initiative came from the Ice Gang team, and they did a really great job! They quickly gathered like-minded people, organised everything to the highest standard and attracted some amazing partners. Among them were residents of the Ice Gang club, as well as the legendary clubs NOT CAP and Chimpers.

The guys put on an incredible broadcast that lasted a full 9 hours, where every viewer could feel the unique atmosphere of the festival.

And you know what's most amazing? Right now, before your very eyes, history is being made.

May this success be just the first step towards new heights. Keep moving forward with the same passion, and we will support and admire your victories. Onward to even greater achievements! ‚ô•Ô∏è
